'''Jooj''' was a [[Killik/Legends|Killik]] hive. They were less than an inch long, and would create swarms of millions. During the [[Swarm War]], they were used as a weapon by the Killiks, having them crawl under enemy armor and kill enemy soldiers via blood sucking. They were a greenish-brown color.

==Appearances==
